data.description: Welcome to Makaha Valley Plantation, where you can make your dream of coastal living a reality without breaking your pocketbook!  Step into this move-in ready 845 sq foot, 2 bedroom second-level unit, and you'll be greeted with a spacious, open floor plan, creating a welcoming atmosphere for everyday living. Plus, with no carpet throughout, cleaning and maintenance are a breeze, leaving you more time to enjoy the island lifestyle.  Nestled in a gated community, you will have peace of mind knowing that security and privacy are top priorities here.  While this is an ideal retreat for those seeking a laid-back, country lifestyle, there is an array of amenities at your fingertips. Take a refreshing dip in one of the two pools, relax in the whirlpools, or stay active and fit utilizing the tennis and basketball courts…there are even kiddie pools too. The best part? The ocean is just a short drive away, allowing you to go for a swim, walk on the beach, or look out for spinner dolphins daily if you desire. This is a wonderful option for first time home buyers, remote workers, a vacation home, or investors.
